data.description: Situated on a quiet street this home has tons of curb appeal and just about everything going for it. There is an attached 2 car garage, a huge completely fenced in backyard with projector screen, back deck and tons of room to run! There is a welcoming covered front porch that leads into the formal dining room, if you don't need a formal space this would make a great area for entertaining. The living room is to the left and the kitchen to the right. Entering the kitchen you'll see that it's nice and bright with an eat in area. The hall leads to a first floor bedroom, full bath and laundry room. At the end of the hall is easy access to the backyard. There is a mudroom coming in from the garage. Upstairs you'll find a full bath and 3 additional bedrooms.
